==軼事==
2011年有報章報導屯門法院大樓外牆維修工程破壞了約15至20個[[小白腰雨燕|小白腰雨燕]]鳥巢，[[香港觀鳥會|香港觀鳥會]]向[[申訴專員公署|申訴專員公署]]投訴，指負責工程的[[建築署|建築署]]及司法機構涉嫌行政失當<ref>{{cite news | title = 屯門法院修外牆　鳥巢被封雨燕枉死兩部門受責 | date = 2011-08-24 | url = http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20110824/15551499 | work = 蘋果日報 | quote =  | accessdate = 2012-05-21 | archive-date = 2015-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150811043023/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20110824/15551499 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 屯門法院涉違法拆燕巢 | date = 2011-08-23 | url = http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110823/00176_032.html | work = 東方日報 | quote =  | accessdate = 2012-05-21 | archive-date = 2015-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150810084201/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110823/00176_032.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

